Who's better than you? No one. You killed everybody else.

Just watch your back. 'Cause if there's one thing I've learned in all my years… nothin' kills a Guardian faster than another Guardian.

Collection.Caption: Invader down! You can relax now!
Invader's dead! Keep pushing.
Hey, you fight dirty. I like it.
Hey, hey, easy there! I think you got 'em! Haha.
YEAH! Hey, you didn't start that fight. You finished it.
They wanted a fight? You gave it to 'em!
Hey! Did you wake up pissed today or something? I like it!
What did they ever do to you?! Just kidding, I dig it!
Woo! You're tearin' it up today!
Ohh, yeah! Look at those hostiles drop!
Line 'em up! Knock 'em down!
Brother, you're showin' 'em how it's done out here!
Do the Vanguard know you're this good? You should be running the place!
All right! You came to fight today!
